589":{"price":2.85,"date":"2026-06-29"}}},{"premise_code":9545,"premise":"THONG HENG CONVENIENCE STORE","type":"Kedai Runcit","prices":{"94":{"price":20,"date":"2026-06-29"},"114":{"price":12.5,"date":"2026-06-29"},"129":{"price":4.5,"date":"2026-06-29"},"917":{"price":3.2,"date":"2026-06-29"},"1558":{"price":9,"date":"2026-06-29"},"1589":{"price":2.85,"date":"2026-06-29"}}},{"premise_code":21923,"premise":"DRAGON HOUSE MINI MART","type":"Pasar Mini","prices":{"114":{"price":9.9,"date":"2026-06-29"},"129":{"price":6.9,"date":"2026-06-29"},"917":{"price":3.9,"date":"2026-06-29"},"918":{"price":2.5,"date":"2026-06-29"},"1558":{"price":14,"date":"2026-06-29"},"1589":{"price":2.85,"date":"2026-06-29"}}},{"premise_code":21925,"premise":"NB JOMBELI FRESH MART PONTIAN","type":"Pasar Mini","prices":{"1":{"price":8.99,"date":"2026-06-29"},"129":{"price":2.49,"date":"2026-06-29"},"917":{"price":3.5,"date":"2026-06-29"},"1109":{"price":14.4,"date":"2026-06-29"},"1589":{"price":2.85,"date":"2026-06-29"}}}]},"local_issues":{"seat":[],"statewide":[{"issue_bm":"Sejak JS-SEZ dimeterai Januari 2025, harga apartmen servis di Johor Bahru melonjak 20.4% dalam setahun — anak muda Puteri Wangsa bergaji ringgit terpaksa bersaing dengan permintaan pelabur rentas sempadan untuk rumah pertama, sampai calon PH sendiri mengaku harga rumah tinggi untuk golongan muda adalah masalah utama di sini.","issue_en":"Since the JS-SEZ was signed in January 2025, Johor Bahru serviced-apartment prices have jumped 20.4% in a single year — young Puteri Wangsa workers earning ringgit are competing with cross-border investor demand for their first home, and even the PH candidate admits high house prices for the young are a top problem here.","receipt_bm":"17 Julai 2025: FMT lapor data JLL Malaysia — harga apartmen servis Johor Bahru naik 20.4% setahun pada S2 2025 (teres dua tingkat +8.6%), didorong momentum JS-SEZ; 30 Jun 2026: Bernama lapor harga rumah tinggi bagi golongan muda antara isu utama di Puteri Wangsa.","receipt_en":"17 July 2025: FMT, citing JLL Malaysia — Johor Bahru serviced-apartment prices up 20.4% year-on-year in Q2 2025 (double-storey terraces +8.6%), driven by JS-SEZ momentum; 30 June 2026: Bernama reports high house prices for young people among the top issues in Puteri Wangsa.","sources":["https://www.freemalaysiatoday.com/category/nation/2025/07/17/johor-bahru-property-prices-surge-on-js-sez-momentum","https://www.bernama.com/radio/news.php?id=2574713","https://iqiglobal.com/blog/johor-real-estate/"],"verdict":"PARTLY_CONFIRMED"},{"issue_bm":"Setahun selepas MB umum pelabur JS-SEZ setuju bayar \"gaji premium\" RM3,500, calon PH Puteri Wangsa sendiri mengaku remaja kita masih cicir sekolah untuk kerja gig atau kerja kasar di Singapura sebab bayarannya tiga kali ganda — dan dia akui kerajaan negeri sahaja tak mampu selesaikannya.","issue_en":"A year after the MB announced JS-SEZ investors agreed to pay RM3,500 \"premium salaries\", PH's own Puteri Wangsa candidate admits local teens are still dropping out of school for gig work or manual jobs in Singapore paying triple — and that the state government alone cannot fix it.","receipt_bm":"30 Jun 2026 (Bernama): Maszlee sebut keciciran pelajaran remaja di Puteri Wangsa dan gaji kerja kasar Singapura \"tiga kali ganda\"; 20 Mei 2025 (Sinar Harian): Onn Hafiz umum pelabur JS-SEZ setuju gaji minimum RM3,500 (diploma) / RM4,000+ (ijazah), bersyarat produktiviti dan kemahiran.","receipt_en":"30 June 2026 (Bernama): Maszlee names teen school dropout in Puteri Wangsa and \"triple\" Singapore manual-job wages; 20 May 2025 (Sinar Harian): Onn Hafiz announced JS-SEZ investors agreed to RM3,500 (diploma) / RM4,000+ (degree) minimum salaries, conditional on productivity and skills.","sources":["https://www.bernama.com/radio/news.php?id=2574713","https://www.sinarharian.com.my/article/729512/edisi/johor/pelabur-js-sez-setuju-tawar-gaji-premium-ndash-onn-hafiz","https://www.thestar.com.my/news/nation/2020/01/02/maszlee-quits-as-education-minister"],"verdict":"PARTLY_CONFIRMED"},{"issue_bm":"Anak muda Muar terpaksa lari ke Singapura sebab gaji di sana tiga kali ganda — 16,930 rakyat Malaysia melepaskan kewarganegaraan pada 2024 sahaja dan lebih 350,000 berulang-alik setiap hari — sedangkan \"gaji premium dari RM3,500\" yang dijanjikan MB semuanya dalam zon JS-SEZ di selatan Johor, 150km dari Muar.","issue_en":"Muar's young people are forced out to Singapore because pay there is roughly triple — 16,930 Malaysians gave up their citizenship in 2024 alone and over 350,000 commute daily — while the MB's promised \"premium salaries from RM3,500\" all sit in JS-SEZ zones in southern Johor, 150km from Muar.","receipt_bm":"Jawapan Parlimen KDN, 11 Ogos 2025: 97,318 rakyat Malaysia jadi warga Singapura 2015–Jun 2025, rekod 16,930 pada 2024; lebih 350,000 ulang-alik ke Singapura setiap hari; janji MB \"gaji premium dari RM3,500\" (Mei 2025) terikat pada 9 zon utama JS-SEZ — kesemuanya di selatan Johor, tiada satu pun di Muar.","receipt_en":"Home Ministry parliamentary reply, 11 Aug 2025: 97,318 Malaysians renounced citizenship for Singapore's between 2015 and June 2025, a record 16,930 in 2024; over 350,000 commute to Singapore daily; the MB's May 2025 \"premium salaries from RM3,500\" pledge is tied to the nine JS-SEZ flagship zones — all in southern Johor, none in Muar.","sources":["https://www.thestar.com.my/news/nation/2025/08/11/nearly-100000-malaysians-renounce-citizenship-for-singapore-in-a-decade-says-home-ministry","https://www.thestar.com.my/metro/metro-news/2025/07/17/johor-stems-brain-drain-to-singapore","https://amro-asia.org/johor-gets-second-chance-at-economic-take-off","https://www.freemalaysiatoday.com/category/nation/2022/05/01/pay-two-thirds-of-singapore-wages-to-keep-locals-home-says-dap-man/"],"verdict":"CONFIRMED"}],"updated":"2026-07-03"},"muda_stances":null}